comment: Plumlee (POR) sets the screen on Brown (BKN) and gives him room to avoid the contact. After the screen, the two players make incidental foot to foot contact that causes Brown to fall to the ground.
Aminu (POR) makes incidental contact with Sloan (BKN) that does not affect his RSBQ.
Plumlee (POR) makes contact with Lopez's (BKN) body as he attempts the layup.
Brown (BKN) makes contact with Plumlee's (POR) arm that affects his shot attempt.
After McCollum (POR) legally contests the jump shot attempt, Sloan (BKN) makes incidental contact with McCollum that causes both players to fall to the ground.
Young (BKN) makes contact with Lillard (POR) with his forearm and affects his driving shot attempt.
Lopez (BKN) uses his arms and continues moving into Aminu (POR) as he sets the screen without giving him room to avoid the contact.
Plumlee (POR) grabs the rebound once the ball is off the rim and outside of the imaginary cylinder above the rim.
Johnson (BKN) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR) prior to the start of his upward shooting motion.
Brown (BKN) sets the screen on Harkless (POR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
McCollum (POR) makes incidental contact with Sloan (BKN) that does not affect his RSBQ.
Lopez (BKN) continues moving as he sets the screen on Harkless (POR) without giving him room to avoid the contact.
Brown (BKN) makes incidental contact with Plumlee (POR) after he secures the rebound.
